      <scopecontent id="aspace_9353c6913134f6f15f7516a19c6239ed">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This is a collection of eighteenth- and nineteenth-century bookplates, mostly European and armorial in style. The bookplates are all mounted on cards measuring 6 x 4.5 inches. Many of the mounts are inscribed with a number in the upper left on recto. A few of the bookplates have additional inscriptions or annotations.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_ccccb129dffcd39edc71e2dd0f41eb19">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into three series: I. Bookplates – Individuals. II. Bookplates – Institutions. III. Ephemera.</p>
         <p>Bookplates are arranged alphabetically within each series.</p>  
      </arrangement>
